 <name>GDE2 Screenshot</name>
 <_summary>A screenshot utility for GDE2 Desktop</_summary>
 <_description>
  <p>
   GDE2 Screenshot is a simple utility that lets you capture screenshots
   of your desktop or of application windows. You can select to copy them
   to the system clipboard or save them in Portable Network Graphics (.png)
   image format.
  </p>
 </_description>
